                        <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">Calculated field:  If all indoor units listed in C01 have C03 == SystemCompliesUsingObservationOfWeighIn  Or SystemCompliesUsingTable150BC Or SystemComplies Or SystemCompliesUsingAlternativeRemedialActions  result = true display term SC System complies with Minimum System Airflow Rate Verification; Else result = false display term SC System does not comply with Minimum System Airflow Rate Verification   and do not allow this Mch-25 to be registered.</xs:documentation>
                        
                     
                     </xs:annotation>
                     
                  
